    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Works comprising outdoor spaces that are designed and often have a relationship to buildings or other constructions. Designs may incorporate plants, water features, and land forms. Landscape design works may be outdoor areas around a built work, large or small parks, gardens, urban developments, and projects for natural restoration by altering or removing built works.</Note_Text>
